508
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:56,940
Untuk kamu, saya akan cepat habis belajar

509
00:38:58,130 --> 00:38:59,660
Jom kita kahwin

510
00:39:34,780 --> 00:39:36,420
Comelnya

511
00:39:36,450 --> 00:39:38,430
Bila nak kahwin

512
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:40,860
Belum cepat lagi

513
00:39:40,910 --> 00:39:43,390
Kami nak ambil gambar dulu

514
00:39:43,810 --> 00:39:45,640
Awal-awal, tahniah untuk kamu berdua

515
00:39:45,710 --> 00:39:46,730
Terima kasih

516
00:39:47,450 --> 00:39:49,160
Dah siap

517
00:40:33,300 --> 00:40:34,590
Kamu memang kacak

518
00:40:35,880 --> 00:40:37,560
Siapa bakal pengantin lelaki ni

519
00:40:38,150 --> 00:40:39,670
Saya punya

520
00:40:40,230 --> 00:40:41,130
Kamu

521
00:40:41,350 --> 00:40:42,400
Kamu panas tak

522
00:40:42,800 --> 00:40:45,340
Sikit, tapi masih okey

523
00:40:46,770 --> 00:40:48,650
Kamu pula, panas tak

524
00:40:48,680 --> 00:40:49,630
Saya tak panas

525
00:40:49,950 --> 00:40:52,500
Kita ambil gambar solo dulu

526
00:40:53,350 --> 00:40:55,030
Siapa dulu

527
00:40:55,530 --> 00:40:57,390
Saya dulu lah

528
00:40:57,470 --> 00:40:58,700
Sini, silakan

529
00:42:25,640 --> 00:42:32,000
(Disember)

530
00:42:37,790 --> 00:42:41,080
Tengok, saya dah kata patut ambil gambar dulu

531
00:42:41,830 --> 00:42:43,820
Lihatlah, comelnya

532
00:42:47,830 --> 00:42:49,350
Nak ambil gambar lagi tak

533
00:42:49,820 --> 00:42:51,400
Saya okey je

534
00:42:52,660 --> 00:42:55,890
Dah sampai sini,
tak nak keluar jalan-jalan ke

535
00:42:56,810 --> 00:42:58,640
Sekarang di Los Angeles musim Krismas

536
00:42:58,740 --> 00:43:01,330
Mungkin ramai orang di mana-mana

537
00:43:01,500 --> 00:43:02,380
Atau

538
00:43:02,480 --> 00:43:04,000
Kita raikan saja di rumah

539
00:43:04,150 --> 00:43:04,950
Atau

540
00:43:05,010 --> 00:43:06,630
Ada tempat yang kamu nak pergi?

541
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:08,840
Tak ada. Aku ikut kamu saja.

542
00:43:09,370 --> 00:43:13,790
Kalau tanya aku, kita duduk rumah saja.

543
00:43:15,100 --> 00:43:17,680
Di luar pun sejuk. Tengok, dah turun salji.

544
00:43:18,560 --> 00:43:20,120
Terlalu sejuk.

545
00:43:25,490 --> 00:43:26,460
Lakonan kamu memang hebat.

546
00:43:26,600 --> 00:43:27,530
Sedikit saja.

547
00:43:28,470 --> 00:43:30,690
Tengok, aku kaku sangat.

548
00:43:31,090 --> 00:43:34,070
Malunya. Aku tak pernah ambil gambar seni.

549
00:43:35,030 --> 00:43:38,320
Biar aku tengok siapa tu.

550
00:43:39,100 --> 00:43:40,550
Mungkin penghantar barang.

551
00:43:49,670 --> 00:43:51,130
P'Jo

552
00:43:51,740 --> 00:43:53,770
Mereka hantar pokok Krismas.

553
00:43:54,010 --> 00:43:55,600
Boleh tolong angkat kejap?

554
00:44:06,640 --> 00:44:10,830
Kamu suka sangat Krismas ya, siap beli pokok.

555
00:44:12,310 --> 00:44:14,560
Aku beli pun lepas dapat izin kamu.

556
00:44:15,230 --> 00:44:16,780
Aku tak komen apa pun.

557
00:44:17,070 --> 00:44:18,970
Tapi tak susahkan ke?

558
00:44:19,700 --> 00:44:21,470
Aku rasa baik kita keluar rumah.

559
00:44:21,530 --> 00:44:23,350
Atau suruh orang hias sekali.

560
00:44:23,360 --> 00:44:25,260
Tak nak. Aku nak hias sendiri.

561
00:44:26,340 --> 00:44:28,030
Jadi, aku bantu kamu

562
00:44:28,300 --> 00:44:30,060
Kena buat apa lagi?

563
00:44:31,610 --> 00:44:34,050
Gantung hiasan dekat pokok tu cukup.

564
00:44:34,320 --> 00:44:35,890
Ada banyak hiasan sini.

565
00:44:36,030 --> 00:44:37,100
Aku beli banyak sangat.

566
00:44:50,020 --> 00:44:52,100
Cantik tak anting-anting baru aku?

567
00:44:55,400 --> 00:44:56,580
Comel gila.

568
00:44:59,430 --> 00:45:01,390
Kamu pandai puji orang.

569
00:45:08,490 --> 00:45:09,600
Letak sini saja.

570
00:45:10,910 --> 00:45:13,510
Kamu rasa benda ni letak mana bagus?

571
00:45:14,530 --> 00:45:18,030
Patut letak sini. Sana dah ada satu besar.

572
00:45:18,200 --> 00:45:19,300
Sini ke?

573
00:45:19,680 --> 00:45:20,790
Tak betul.

574
00:45:22,380 --> 00:45:24,260
- Tak berapa elok
- Terlalu rendah ke?

575
00:45:24,570 --> 00:45:25,790
- Kalau sini?
- Sini boleh.

576
00:45:48,610 --> 00:45:50,690
Nak ajak aku pergi mana?

577
00:45:51,190 --> 00:45:52,770
Aku dah sediakan hadiah untuk kamu.

578
00:45:53,080 --> 00:45:54,140
Hadiah apa?

579
00:45:56,890 --> 00:45:58,870
Game baru ke?

580
00:46:00,220 --> 00:46:03,110
Tapi sekarang tak ada game baru keluar pun.

581
00:46:03,230 --> 00:46:05,440
Eh, emas ke tu?

582
00:46:05,700 --> 00:46:08,050
P'Jo, aku memang suka emas!

583
00:46:08,670 --> 00:46:09,700
Bukanlah.

584
00:46:09,900 --> 00:46:12,040
- Eh
- Aku nak lepaskan tangan

585
00:46:23,720 --> 00:46:25,820
Mesin tangkap anak patung ke?

586
00:46:26,230 --> 00:46:27,290
Ya.

587
00:46:28,280 --> 00:46:30,440
Sebab masa kita couple, ada orang kata nak hadiah.

588
00:46:30,600 --> 00:46:32,520
Jadi, aku beli mesin tangkap tu untuk kamu.

589
00:46:32,970 --> 00:46:34,020
Comel, kan?

590
00:46:35,270 --> 00:46:38,500
Ingatkan emas tadi.

591
00:46:42,280 --> 00:46:44,530
P'Jo, aku gurau saja.

592
00:46:44,930 --> 00:46:46,500
Ini memang comel tau.

593
00:46:46,740 --> 00:46:47,730
Tapi kenapa

594
00:46:47,920 --> 00:46:50,540
Dalam cuma ada seekor kura-kura.

595
00:46:52,850 --> 00:46:54,950
Mungkin staff lupa ambil. Aku nak komplen.

596
00:46:54,950 --> 00:46:56,210
Tak perlu. Tak apa.

597
00:46:56,610 --> 00:46:58,900
Aku rasa comel jugalah.

598
00:47:00,510 --> 00:47:02,660
Malam ni aku nak tangkap dia.

599
00:47:03,880 --> 00:47:04,960
Aku nak mulakan!

600
00:47:08,040 --> 00:47:09,120
Jom mula!

601
00:47:17,580 --> 00:47:18,710
Hey

602
00:47:19,340 --> 00:47:21,330
Hey P'Jo

603
00:47:21,500 --> 00:47:22,830
Aku dah dapat tangkap.

604
00:47:22,900 --> 00:47:23,860
Sekali cuba terus kena.

605
00:47:23,870 --> 00:47:25,070
Hey

606
00:47:28,100 --> 00:47:29,350
P'Jo, comelnya benda ni!

607
00:47:30,440 --> 00:47:32,160
Lagi buruk dari itik itu.

608
00:47:32,160 --> 00:47:33,150
Hey

609
00:47:33,190 --> 00:47:34,260
Mana ada.

610
00:47:34,710 --> 00:47:35,820
Comel sangat tau!

611
00:47:39,490 --> 00:47:42,800
Jomlah, P'Jo, kamu dah janji.

612
00:47:42,870 --> 00:47:44,310
Jomlah!

613
00:47:47,110 --> 00:47:48,350
Biar aku tolong pakaikan, pusing sikit.

614
00:47:59,020 --> 00:48:00,240
Tak cukup lagi.

615
00:48:01,580 --> 00:48:02,990
Kena pakai yang ini juga.

616
00:48:10,510 --> 00:48:11,910
Memang comel.

617
00:48:18,430 --> 00:48:19,480
Kenapa gelak?

618
00:48:19,740 --> 00:48:20,890
Sebab

619
00:48:21,150 --> 00:48:23,940
Lepas pakai apron, kamu terlalu comel.

620
00:48:24,620 --> 00:48:26,180
Biar aku tengok.

621
00:48:26,430 --> 00:48:27,870
Biar aku tengok kamu ambil apa.

622
00:48:28,860 --> 00:48:30,450
Dah tengok tak boleh padam tau.

623
00:48:35,610 --> 00:48:37,590
Kamu ambil gambar pun elok.

624
00:48:38,000 --> 00:48:39,040
Terima kasih.

625
00:48:39,340 --> 00:48:41,210
Jom kita mula.

626
00:48:42,370 --> 00:48:43,770
- Jomlah
- Jadi

627
00:48:43,890 --> 00:48:45,050
Aku mula dari mana dulu?

628
00:48:45,390 --> 00:48:47,300
Mula-mula pecahkan telur.

629
00:48:47,860 --> 00:48:50,070
Pecahkan, kemudian kacau sebati.

630
00:48:51,650 --> 00:48:53,850
Biskut je kot, beli siap pun murah.

631
00:48:54,560 --> 00:48:55,510
Apa kamu cakap tadi?

632
00:48:55,520 --> 00:48:57,090
Tak ada apa.

633
00:48:57,560 --> 00:49:00,100
- Pecahkan telur dulu kan? Ketuk dulu?
- Ya, betul.

634
00:49:01,770 --> 00:49:03,270
P'Jo, ketuk tepi mangkuk tu.

635
00:49:04,840 --> 00:49:07,390
Cangkang telur masuk pula.

636
00:49:11,040 --> 00:49:13,990
P'Jo, kena kacau macam ni.

637
00:49:14,090 --> 00:49:17,500
Aku tunjuk, satu dua tiga, kacau begini.

638
00:49:18,610 --> 00:49:21,150
Buat sekali lagi.

639
00:49:21,800 --> 00:49:23,300
Kacau saja.

640
00:49:23,560 --> 00:49:24,830
Kamu nakal lagi.

641
00:49:25,560 --> 00:49:28,880
Tengok, dia bergurau lagi.

642
00:49:31,150 --> 00:49:33,030
Tak adalah.

643
00:49:38,890 --> 00:49:41,250
Sedap gila, biskut kamu memang sedap.

644
00:49:41,260 --> 00:49:42,840
Aku tak buat apa pun.

645
00:49:42,890 --> 00:49:44,630
Aku cuma campur semua saja.

646
00:49:44,710 --> 00:49:47,300
Betul ke? Tapi sedap sangat.

647
00:49:48,320 --> 00:49:49,650
Ya.

648
00:49:50,070 --> 00:49:51,400
Sekelip mata saja

649
00:49:51,550 --> 00:49:53,510
Kita dah setahun bersama.

650
00:49:53,510 --> 00:49:54,920
Jom kita imbas semula.

651
00:49:55,000 --> 00:49:55,730
Tahun ni

652
00:49:55,810 --> 00:49:57,060
Apa yang dah kita lalui bersama?

653
00:49:57,950 --> 00:49:59,360
Kamu rasa bagaimana?

654
00:49:59,610 --> 00:50:00,700
Setahun ni bagi kamu macam mana?

655
00:50:03,180 --> 00:50:06,150
Dengan kamu, tahun ni paling terbaik dalam hidup aku.

656
00:50:06,240 --> 00:50:07,600
Kamu pula?

657
00:50:07,760 --> 00:50:08,920
Aku pun sama.

658
00:50:10,270 --> 00:50:12,530
Tahun ni sungguh luar biasa.

659
00:50:12,620 --> 00:50:14,170
Banyak sangat benda berlaku.

660
00:50:14,460 --> 00:50:15,230
Mula-mula dulu

661
00:50:15,240 --> 00:50:16,350
Aku bangun dari tidur

662
00:50:16,600 --> 00:50:17,990
Terus berhutang banyak.

663
00:50:18,300 --> 00:50:19,390
Tapi akhirnya

664
00:50:19,510 --> 00:50:22,310
Tak sangka, si penagih hutang jadi teman lelaki aku.

665
00:50:22,310 --> 00:50:23,180
Haha

666
00:50:26,680 --> 00:50:29,350
Hari ni aku nak tanya kamu satu soalan.

667
00:50:30,570 --> 00:50:31,520
Apa dia?

668
00:50:32,720 --> 00:50:35,670
Kalau kamu ada tiga hajat,

669
00:50:35,960 --> 00:50:37,080
Apa kamu nak minta?

670
00:50:37,080 --> 00:50:38,090
Tiga hajat ya?

671
00:50:38,840 --> 00:50:40,180
Aku nak serahkan semua hajat aku pada kamu.

672
00:50:40,500 --> 00:50:41,860
Jadi aku ada enam hajat lah?

673
00:50:41,890 --> 00:50:42,780
Ya.

674
00:50:44,070 --> 00:50:45,250
Hajat apa nak minta ya?

675
00:50:46,680 --> 00:50:51,250
Aku harap syarikat game kegemaran aku

676
00:50:51,500 --> 00:50:53,280
keluarkan banyak game baru.

677
00:50:53,450 --> 00:50:54,200
Lepas tu

678
00:50:54,280 --> 00:50:56,730
Harap aku ada duit nak beli semua tu.

679
00:50:56,730 --> 00:50:59,210
Moga ada masa nak main.

680
00:50:59,540 --> 00:51:03,920
Aku nak aku, kamu dan mak

681
00:51:04,800 --> 00:51:07,380
dan semua orang sekeliling kita bahagia.

682
00:51:08,580 --> 00:51:11,140
Akhir sekali

683
00:51:11,570 --> 00:51:13,300
Aku harap boleh menang loteri.

684
00:51:13,470 --> 00:51:14,950
Hadiah kecil pun tak apa.

685
00:51:15,100 --> 00:51:17,170
Kamu teringin sangat menang loteri ya?

686
00:51:17,860 --> 00:51:20,810
- Nak hadiah kedua tak? Aku bagi kamu.
- Wah!

687
00:51:20,980 --> 00:51:22,470
Kamu tak faham.

688
00:51:22,590 --> 00:51:23,700
Hajat aku adalah

689
00:51:23,720 --> 00:51:25,530
bantu keluarga cari duit.

690
00:51:26,080 --> 00:51:28,660
Kalau kamu yang bagi

691
00:51:28,760 --> 00:51:30,740
bukankah itu pun duit family?

692
00:51:31,490 --> 00:51:33,070
Yeke? Aku tak faham benda tu.

693
00:51:33,280 --> 00:51:35,480
Ada soalan lain lagi nak tanya?

694
00:51:38,300 --> 00:51:40,510
Aku nak tanya

695
00:51:40,690 --> 00:51:43,300
Ada tak apa-apa yang kamu nak aku ubah?

696
00:51:43,450 --> 00:51:46,640
Atau bahagian mana kamu tak suka tentang aku?

697
00:51:46,880 --> 00:51:49,050
Tak ada. Kamu pula?

698
00:51:49,480 --> 00:51:50,640
Aku ke?

699
00:51:50,810 --> 00:51:52,660
Kalau nak ubah

700
00:51:53,550 --> 00:51:56,100
Aku nak jadi lebih matang sikit.

701
00:51:56,180 --> 00:51:58,090
Aku rasa aku suka bergurau dan macam budak-budak.

702
00:52:01,730 --> 00:52:04,240
Maksud aku, kamu nak aku ubah kat mana?

703
00:52:05,540 --> 00:52:07,670
Tengok, aku bergurau lagi.

704
00:52:09,600 --> 00:52:10,710
Kamu ke?

705
00:52:12,060 --> 00:52:13,320
Aku rasa

706
00:52:13,810 --> 00:52:15,200
Tak perlu ubah apa-apa pun.

707
00:52:15,200 --> 00:52:17,210
Sebab kamu dah cukup sempurna sekarang.

708
00:52:19,110 --> 00:52:21,080
Soalan terakhir

709
00:52:22,230 --> 00:52:25,660
Ada tak soalan yang kamu takut nak tanya aku?

710
00:52:29,340 --> 00:52:30,790
Setiap kali aku pandang kamu

711
00:52:30,870 --> 00:52:32,430
Mesti ada satu soalan dalam hati aku

712
00:52:33,610 --> 00:52:34,530
Apa dia?

713
00:52:36,610 --> 00:52:38,590
Siapa budak ni?

714
00:52:38,790 --> 00:52:40,090
Dia asal dari mana?

715
00:52:40,290 --> 00:52:42,060
Kenapa aku sayang sangat kat dia?

716
00:52:43,280 --> 00:52:44,760
Aku pun sama.

717
00:52:45,230 --> 00:52:47,270
Aku pun ada satu soalan.

718
00:52:48,240 --> 00:52:50,390
Siapa sebenarnya dia ni?

719
00:52:50,670 --> 00:52:53,130
Dia buat aku gembira tiap hari. Siapa hantar dia?

720
00:53:01,130 --> 00:53:03,360
Tiap-tiap tahun temankan aku macam ni, ya?

721
00:53:03,360 --> 00:53:05,690
Sambut Krismas dan Tahun Baru sama-sama.

722
00:53:06,570 --> 00:53:07,930
Sentiasa bersama.

723
00:53:10,180 --> 00:53:11,200
Baik.

724
00:53:12,050 --> 00:53:13,890
Aku akan bersama kamu selamanya.

725
00:53:37,370 --> 00:53:39,070
Kamu suka yang mana lebih?

726
00:53:40,840 --> 00:53:42,420
Saya suka kedua-duanya.

727
00:53:42,560 --> 00:53:45,060
Dan kedua-duanya kamu yang beri.

728
00:53:46,030 --> 00:53:46,720
Oh ya.

729
00:53:46,850 --> 00:53:49,690
Kenapa kamu tak suka itik bodoh ni?

730
00:53:52,000 --> 00:53:55,390
Itik ni hadiah pertama dari kamu.

731
00:53:55,610 --> 00:53:58,230
Masa tu kita pun belum saling kenal.

732
00:53:58,740 --> 00:54:00,630
Sebab ini hadiah yang pertama.

733
00:54:00,810 --> 00:54:03,110
Sebenarnya aku nak beli hadiah lebih baik.

734
00:54:03,750 --> 00:54:04,570
Jadi...

735
00:54:04,810 --> 00:54:06,810
Apa yang tak kena dengan itik bodoh ni?

736
00:54:06,960 --> 00:54:08,420
Tengoklah muka dia.

737
00:54:09,040 --> 00:54:10,700
Kamu pun panggil dia itik bodoh.

738
00:54:10,790 --> 00:54:12,990
Nampak bodoh, tapi comel juga bodohnya.

739
00:54:14,030 --> 00:54:16,980
Hanya mak sendiri saja kata dia comel.

740
00:54:17,210 --> 00:54:20,300
Kesian betul, biar aku tengok.

741
00:54:20,470 --> 00:54:22,340
Apa? Ayah kamu tak sayang kamu?

742
00:54:22,500 --> 00:54:23,860
Apa?

743
00:54:24,700 --> 00:54:26,880
Sebab ayah cuma boleh cinta mak.

744
00:54:27,840 --> 00:54:28,960
P'Jo

745
00:54:29,020 --> 00:54:31,240
Kenapa ni? Nak main rumah-rumahan ke?

746
00:54:32,670 --> 00:54:34,100
Baik aku tidur sajalah.

747
00:54:40,620 --> 00:54:42,070
Cium sekali lagi.

748
00:54:42,350 --> 00:54:44,110
Cium sepanjang hari.

